+- Update pom.xml files in sync-data modules to depend on infra modules
+- Update pom.xml files in admin-listener modules to depend on infra modules
+- Update pom.xml files in registry modules to depend on infra modules
+- Update pom.xml files in plugin modules to depend on shenyu-infra-redis
+
+### 2. Update Imports Across Codebase
+- Replace imports from old package paths to new infra packages
+- Update EtcdClient imports to use `org.apache.shenyu.infra.etcd.client.EtcdClient`
+- Update RedisConfigProperties imports to use `org.apache.shenyu.infra.redis.RedisProperties`
+- Update NacosConfig imports to use `org.apache.shenyu.infra.nacos.config.NacosConfig`
+
+### 3. Remove Duplicate Code
+- Delete duplicate EtcdClient from sync-data-etcd
+- Delete duplicate EtcdClient from registry-etcd
+- Delete duplicate EtcdClient from admin-listener-etcd
+- Delete duplicate RedisConfigProperties from plugin modules
+- Delete duplicate RedisConnectionFactory from plugin modules
+- Delete duplicate NacosConfig from sync-data-nacos
+
+### 4. Update Spring Boot Auto-Configuration
+- Add spring.factories files to infra modules for auto-configuration
+- Update existing auto-configuration classes to use infra modules
+- Ensure conditional annotations work correctly
+
+### 5. Update Configuration Property Classes
+- Update EtcdProperties in admin-listener to use EtcdConfig from infra
+- Update NacosProperties in admin-listener to use NacosConfig from infra
+- Ensure all @ConfigurationProperties annotations use correct prefixes from InfraConstants
+
+### 6. Testing
+- Verify module dependencies resolve correctly
+- Test that conditional annotations activate beans properly
+- Run full build: `mvn clean install -DskipTests`
+- Run tests: `mvn test`
+- Verify no compilation errors
+
+### 7. Documentation
+- Update module README files
+- Document migration guide for users
+- Add examples of using builder patterns
+
+## Usage Examples
+
+### EtcdConfig with Builder
+```java
+EtcdConfig config = EtcdConfig.builder()
+    .url("http://localhost:2379")
+    .sessionTimeout(3000)
+    .connectionTimeout(3000)
+    .serializer("json")
+    .build();
+```
+
+### NacosConfig with Builder
+```java
+NacosACMConfig acm = NacosACMConfig.builder()
+    .enabled(true)
+    .endpoint("acm.aliyun.com")
+    .namespace("public")
+    .accessKey("your-access-key")
+    .secretKey("your-secret-key")
+    .build();
+
+NacosConfig config = NacosConfig.builder()
+    .url("localhost:8848")
+    .namespace("shenyu")
+    .username("nacos")
+    .password("nacos")
+    .contextPath("/nacos")
+    .acm(acm)
+    .build();
+```
+
+### Using Conditional Annotations
+```java
+@Configuration
+@ConditionalOnSyncEtcd
+public class EtcdSyncDataConfiguration {
+
+    @Bean
+    public SyncDataService etcdSyncDataService(EtcdConfig etcdConfig) {
+        // This bean will only be created if shenyu.sync.etcd.url is configured
+        return new EtcdSyncDataService(etcdConfig);
+    }
+}
+```
+
+### Using Unified EtcdClient
+```java
+// For sync-data or admin-listener (no lease management)
+Client client = Client.builder().endpoints(url).build();
+EtcdClient etcdClient = new EtcdClient(client);
+
+// For registry (with lease management for ephemeral nodes)
+EtcdClient etcdClient = new EtcdClient("http://localhost:2379", 30, 3000);
+etcdClient.putEphemeral("/shenyu/service/my-service", "service-data");
+```
+
