+## Conclusion
+
+This refactoring establishes a solid foundation for centralized infrastructure management in ShenYu. The new module structure promotes:
+- **Code Reusability:** Shared infrastructure code across all modules
+- **Maintainability:** Single source of truth for infrastructure clients
+- **Consistency:** Standardized configuration patterns and naming
+- **Extensibility:** Easy to add new infrastructure modules following the same pattern
+
+The work completed represents the core infrastructure refactoring. The remaining steps involve updating module dependencies and imports throughout the codebase, which can be done incrementally without breaking existing functionality.
